 are you Quellious?' I said 'Sha' just then when I was awake again I looked to my side, there was a sword into my side, I turned around and saw guard tolus with an icy glare on his face 'Shando! how could you kill my own father!!' the Tier`Dal quickly rushed to me and and pushed the human away, luckily my mend skills had had came back, I closed  the wounds, and took the sword in my hands, the sword evaporated, the power of my fists was amazing, with a few blows I had tolus down cold, he could not get up, I looked at my fists and wondered.. 'shando, hurry, my fellow Tier'Dal has an idea'<br>
<br>
